0Z","msg":"事實係...<br />\n星期六日係戰場<br />\n星期一至五大家如常番工......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry 放負"},{"pid":"0a78a9479ffa50dc495ead29326201ba06d811f6","tid":1691574,"uid":254020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:33:15.000Z","msg":"甴曱平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e739669a34a1f8ffd73c48eed1479b104a69ab","tid":1691574,"uid":8710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:35:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ea9d59f7cff9aab8d85f2cba9447743f22642ad","tid":1691574,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:36:05.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d6729db31fc3548b78d3ee2dceb6fb726f0d5cde","tid":1691574,"uid":156341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:36:28.000Z","msg":"生活如常<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fdd35565c4370a93a68f0f119d2127c95931c8e","tid":1691574,"uid":156341,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:37:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢竟然影到香港人既平衡時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"9a7852c12bec9544348d6c9b445ecf3ab5d050b5","tid":1691574,"uid":67424,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2019/11/01/world/00hk-diptych-04left/merlin_162694671_9f118fa1-d6c6-41f6-b93d-1a6ed4a6014b-superJumbo.jpg?quality=90&amp;auto=webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.nyt.com%2Fimages%2F2019%2F11%2F01%2Fworld%2F00hk-diptych-04left%2Fmerlin_162694671_9f118fa1-d6c6-41f6-b93d-1a6ed4a6014b-superJumbo.jpg%3Fquality%3D90%26auto%3Dwebp&h=294801f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2019/11/01/world/00hk-diptych-01right/merlin_163157388_eceac45e-ad59-40c4-a5e4-095bb04d541d-superJumbo.jpg?quality=90&amp;auto=webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.nyt.com%2Fimages%2F2019%2F11%2F01%2Fworld%2F00hk-diptych-01right%2Fmerlin_163157388_eceac45e-ad59-40c4-a5e4-095bb04d541d-superJumbo.jpg%3Fquality%3D90%26auto%3Dwebp&h=5442121f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019/10/14: 盼望<br />\n<br />\n過往五個月，我地創造左歷史，有邊個會諗到雨革後會有流水革命，只要我地繼續秉持不分不割，檢討反省既原則，堅持落去一定會有曙光<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"85ebc99a406e1c37ce17df4bdf66709675cfe12c","tid":1691574,"uid":1241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:48:08.000Z","msg":"睇怕相入面手足都潛咗唔少<br />\n希望將來煲底再見到你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae963e012a1058ace7fafc6c95c4ebe1443ae89","tid":1691574,"uid":13176,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a884e226c750c1eb9f110ce73363f57fd18a3a23","tid":1691574,"uid":261699,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:06:10.000Z","msg":"驀然回首<br />\n恍如隔世"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:13:03.000Z","msg":"睇到d相不禁悲從中來。<br />\n<br />\n我相信時至今日依然好多人信念不變，甚至比起五個月前更加憤怒悲傷，發揮各人所長去抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n但，相中手足還安好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五個月來被跳樓被浮屍被雞姦被車撞被槍傷既不計其數，尤其今晚發生區議員被咬甩耳仔、夫婦被刀斬至命危......<br />\n<br />\n有時會諗行動點解越嚟越少人，的確。但隨住極權政府而家不論和勇都通通照「解決」。<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻我只係諗，相中人有多少個還健在？還活著嗎，沒受傷嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留下既人其實都好煎熬好痛苦，究竟黎明何時來到。但為咗一切一切既人事物，我地唔可以輸！一輸，就輸成個香港。<br />\n<br />\n附上張圖鼓勵下大家，唯有勝利，所有犧牲先唔會白費。謹記煲底之約，一齊贏，共勉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S1eBso6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS1eBso6.jpg&h=37e8ff16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44f09faccc7686e2f2f2097aa6a92b2bec54728f","tid":1691574,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:14:57.000Z","msg":"甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[日常文宣] [文宣方向] 以子之矛，攻子之盾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0c639ded3bccb196579b9438c0080f43b950a6e9","tid":1691574,"uid":261699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ae963e012a1058ace7fafc6c95c4ebe1443ae89","tid":1691574,"uid":13176,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a884e226c750c1eb9f110ce73363f57fd18a3a23","tid":1691574,"uid":261699,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:06:10.000Z","msg":"驀然回首<br />\n恍如隔世"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:13:03.000Z","msg":"睇到d相不禁悲從中來。<br />\n<br />\n我相信時至今日依然好多人信念不變，甚至比起五個月前更加憤怒悲傷，發揮各人所長去抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n但，相中手足還安好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五個月來被跳樓被浮屍被雞姦被車撞被槍傷既不計其數，尤其今晚發生區議員被咬甩耳仔、夫婦被刀斬至命危......<br />\n<br />\n有時會諗行動點解越嚟越少人，的確。但隨住極權政府而家不論和勇都通通照「解決」。<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻我只係諗，相中人有多少個還健在？還活著嗎，沒受傷嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留下既人其實都好煎熬好痛苦，究竟黎明何時來到。但為咗一切一切既人事物，我地唔可以輸！一輸，就輸成個香港。<br />\n<br />\n附上張圖鼓勵下大家，唯有勝利，所有犧牲先唔會白費。謹記煲底之約，一齊贏，共勉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S1eBso6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS1eBso6.jpg&h=37e8ff16&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"呢場&ldquo;戰爭&rdquo;可能要長時間先會完<br />\n受到傷害甚至死亡嘅手足<br />\n可能要好似猶太集中營或台灣228咁<br />\n即使得到道歉<br />\n好多年後依然無法忘記傷痛<br />\n而我地除咗盡畢生能力記住呢幾個月發生嘅事<br />\n同對抗中共外<br />\n好難再做到咩彌補到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7207f2ca90f5bf2e1f6a72a387d7b5ff26fb3a3f","tid":1691574,"uid":67424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T23:19:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ecc8bae4d66e46c4aa8ecaf30a6a6a9b7e257a6e","tid":1691574,"uid":67424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T23:30:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"268aa31e8a1cbddd88926eb842e122a183a3ff10","tid":1691574,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T23:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79692e95a665934dcdd80accb4091c96362d0141","tid":1691574,"uid":67424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T23:59:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"46410272dd6d4009b9731d87ed7a138f9e44da48","tid":1691574,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T23:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef00609ef2e7a62f385856f7b6a67222c12c72f6","tid":1691574,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:16:02.000Z","msg":"香港好似人格分裂咁"},{"pid":"93c8de5bf9588a113c1008a8e3a8786e64f6661e","tid":1691574,"uid":35457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:20:27.000Z","msg":"睇到啲相唔知點解好似對相入邊既手足有種好相熟既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3aea01130012f7a92939cdea264675c6f23202","tid":1691574,"uid":15658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:21:05.000Z","msg":"我覺得應該叫平行時空"},{"pid":"f9a1a778ec8b437d843a157b2d89f629167351ef","tid":1691574,"uid"